OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FSome targets for mental health care
OL,7,Fhave been removed from formal
OL,8,Finstructions due to be issued to NHS
OL,9,Fbosses this Thursday, ITV News
OL,10,Funderstands.
OL,12,FIt has also been claimed that there
OL,13,Fwill be no clear plan to tackle the
OL,14,Fwaiting lists for mental health,
OL,15,Fdespite a clear focus on those waiting
OL,16,Ffor physical procedures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
