OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FThere are fears that the NHS Planning
OL,7,FGuidance will not include specific
OL,8,Fgoals linked to areas such as the
OL,9,Fspeed at which those suffering with
OL,10,Feating disorders are seen.
OL,12,FThere is also a question mark about
OL,13,Fwhether a target on the percentage of
OL,14,Fpeople with severe mental illness
OL,15,Freceiving a full annual physical
OL,16,Fhealth check will remain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
