OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fwants to give health bosses more
OL,8,Ffreedom over how they spend their
OL,9,Ffunds, but there are fears the heavy
OL,10,Ffocus on one umbrella target will
OL,11,Freduce care in other areas.
OL,13,FThe government's headline target is to
OL,14,Fensure that 92% of patients get
OL,15,Froutine operations within 18 weeks -
OL,16,Fwhich focuses entirely on physical
OL,17,Fhealth.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, some are warning funding
OL,20,Fcould also be affected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
