OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FThe government is committed to a
OL,7,Fringfence on mental health funding
OL,8,F(after a major backlash at the
OL,9,Fsuggestion it could be removed) called
OL,10,Fthe Mental Health Investment Standard
OL,11,F(MHIS).
OL,13,FIt ensures the percentage spent on
OL,14,Fmental health increases in line with
OL,15,Ftotal NHS funding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
