OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FThere are also concerns a second
OL,7,Fcommitment from the previous
OL,8,FConservative government - to go
OL,9,Ffurther and actually increase the
OL,10,Fshare of the NHS budget that goes on
OL,11,Fmental health year on year - could be
OL,12,Fwatered down.
OL,14,FThe aim of that pledge is to try to
OL,15,Fachieve parity between mental and
OL,16,Fphysical health as promised by the
OL,17,Fgovernment in its election manifesto.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
