OL,6,FSources have insisted to me that it is
OL,7,Fthreatened - and will not be
OL,8,Fspecifically outlined in the planning
OL,9,Fguidance.
OL,11,FHowever, a Department of Health source
OL,12,Fdenied the rising share of funding was
OL,13,Funder threat, arguing that the
OL,14,Finclusion of the MHIS meant NHS bosses
OL,15,Fwould be instructed to increase share
OL,16,Fof spend.
