OL,6,FI'm also told that the planning
OL,7,Fguidance fails to include information
OL,8,Fon "assertive outreach investment"
OL,9,Fthat could be used to try to prevent
OL,10,Fcases in which mentally ill
OL,11,Findividuals commit terrible crimes.
OL,13,FLast year health providers were asked
OL,14,Fto conduct a review of services for
OL,15,Fpeople like Valdo Calocane - a
OL,16,Fparanoid schizophrenic who fatally
OL,17,Fstabbed three people in Nottingham.
