OL,11,FThe government source said priority
OL,12,Fareas were waiting times for electives
OL,13,F(physical procedures), A&E,
OL,14,Fambulances, seeing GPs and dentists -
OL,15,Fbut also "the mental health of the
OL,16,Fnation". He insisted that mental
OL,17,Fhealth would be a focus on the
OL,18,Fguidance.
