OL,3,CNHS mental health targets could be
OL,4,Cstripped back 'with no clear plan'
OL,6,FMark Winstanley, chief executive of
OL,7,FRethink Mental Illness, said: "There
OL,8,Fare around 1.6 million people waiting
OL,9,Fon treatment for mental ill health in
OL,10,Fthe community and this will only cause
OL,11,Fthem to get further from work, so it
OL,12,Fis vital that access to community care
OL,13,Fand crisis care is prioritised."
OL,15,FOn physical health checks, the Royal
OL,16,FCollege of Psychiatrists warned last
OL,17,FAutumn that 87,000 people with a
OL,18,Fsevere mental illness died from a
OL,19,Fpreventable physical health condition
OL,20,Fin three years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
