OL,6,FThey pointed out that the life
OL,7,Fexpectancy of people with bipolar
OL,8,Fdisorder or schizophrenia is 15 to 20
OL,9,Fyears lower than for the general
OL,10,Fpopulation - with respiratory disease,
OL,11,Fheart disease and liver disease among
OL,12,Fthe key causes.
